#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int t,n,x,y,c,i;
    scanf("%d%d",&t,&n);
    while(t--)
    {
              scanf("%d%d",&x,&y);
              c=0;
              int a[1000];
              while(x!=1||y!=1)
              {
                               if(x==y)
                               {  a[c]=x;c++; x/=2;y/=2;}
                               else if(x>y)
                               { x/=2;}
                               else
                               y/=2;
              }
              a[c]=1;c++;
              for(i=c-1;i>=0;i--)
              printf("%d ",a[i]);
              printf("\n");
    }
    return 0;
}
